### Test AWG API

### Get Latest Sensor Data (now includes alerts)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/sensor/latest

### Get Readings (last 10)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/sensor/readings?limit=10

### Predict Fill Time
GET http://localhost:5000/api/sensor/predict/fillTime

### Get Fill History
GET http://localhost:5000/api/sensor/history

### Get All Alerts
GET http://localhost:5000/api/sensor/alerts

### Mark Alerts as Read
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/sensor/alerts/read

